Lemon Test: The US approach. 
======================================================
incremental:true


1. The statute must not advance nor inhibit religious practice (also known as the Effect Prong)

2. The statute must have non-religious purpose. (also known as the Purpose Prong)

3. The statute must not result in an "excessive government entanglement" with religious affairs. (also known as the Entanglement Prong)


